    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🤖 Phase 2: The Smart Mailbox Worker\n\n**Goal: Take care of daily chores and help with email replies.**\n\nWhile the Organizer sorts your mail instantly, the Worker handles the \"heavy lifting\" on a schedule. It acts like a quiet helper that cleans up your trash and gets your personal replies ready so you don't have to start from scratch.\n\n### ✨ What it does for you:\n* 🧹 **The Janitor:** Automatically finds emails labeled as \"To-Be-Trashed\" and moves to \"Trash\", once they are 7 days old.\n\n* ✍️ **The Assistant:** Checks for new \"Personal\" emails and writes a warm, human-friendly draft reply for you, with signs off with your name.\n\n* ⏳ **Smart Timing:** Runs once a day (or whenever you choose) to stay efficient without hitting any limits.",
